Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:43.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}遗失了开启乐园的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:48.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}接受惩罚死去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:52.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}向着深夜的迷途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.40,0:22:57.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}无法忍受的荆棘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.02,0:23:01.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}松开的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.62,0:23:11.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}追寻着永远被埋葬的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:20.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要看这残破的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:29.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}破裂的牵绊 黑色的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:39.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要来这里 这你未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.57,0:23:46.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}下着绝望的雨的世界……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.55,0:23:47.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}现在、完结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.13,0:23:53.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}如火焰般闪耀于汝等心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:55.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}主宰汝等…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:43.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}楽園の扉開く　鍵を　失くして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.18,0:22:48.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}罰を受けし心は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:52.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}夜の迷路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.40,0:22:57.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}茨の王　赦さず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.02,0:23:01.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}解けめ鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.62,0:23:11.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}求めたのは　永遠　埋めたは愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:20.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}穢れ壊れた　僕をみないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:29.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}裂かれた絆　黒きレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:39.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}ここにこないで　君は知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.57,0:23:46.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}絶望の雨が降れる　世界が……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.55,0:23:47.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}今、終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.13,0:23:53.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}Which Shinetu as a flame in the midst of your palace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:55.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}And reigneth Amongst…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:33.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}月亮在轻轻低语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:38.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}以谁也听不到的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:42.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur3}不断满涨的潮水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:46.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}消失渐远的记忆中的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:52.03,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}星星在密密记述着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:56.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}以谁也无法解读的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:01.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}无限的语言的涡旋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:06.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}千亿本书由此诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:13.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}我的天空无限广阔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:18.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}时间在飞速的镌刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:24.56,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}毫无所知的虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:27.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}汇聚的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:31.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}也只能在泥土中枯朽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:38.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}即使如此我仍在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:43.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}扬起晦涩难懂的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:49.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}至少将这声音传至天际
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:54.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}太阳也终会升起吧
